#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:2 cbca583923424e10909fed6c857a8d45
msgid "安信可 LoRa/LoRaWan系列模块 FAQ"
msgstr "Ai-Thinker LoRa/LoRaWAN Series Module FAQ"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:17 23b81bf0fcda4093a7468c49f6c6b7f2
msgid "Ra-01模块和Ra-02模块的区别是什么？"
msgstr "What is the difference between the Ra-01 module and the Ra-02 module?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:18 d4fd80c883a242ecba424d3284da454e
msgid "答：Ra-01，Ra-02内部只有一个SX1278芯片，两者的区别就是一个天线座子（Ra-02多了一个Ipex座子）"
msgstr "A: Both Ra-01 and Ra-02 have only one SX1278 chip inside. The difference is the antenna connector. Ra-02 has an additional IPEX connector."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:21 1b092b70744d4746a9d78dc6f3aff8d5
msgid "RHF78-052模块用OTAA入网模式失败了，显示join failed 有什么办法去定位失败原因吗?"
msgstr "The RHF78-052 module failed to join the network in OTAA mode and shows \"join failed\". Is there any way to locate the cause of the failure?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:22 b71fdfc8d06a4478a2631bafcb67345b
msgid "AT+CH=CN470 设置为该地区信道"
msgstr "Set the channel for this region with AT+CH=CN470."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:25 632595b78b51476b84031ae1d3e17785
msgid "SX1278有寻址或数据加密功能吗?是不是别人的1278只要与我同频就可以收到所有数据?"
msgstr "Does SX1278 support addressing or data encryption? If another SX1278 is on the same frequency as mine, can it receive all my data?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:26 b69d7be1e5b24808996ccfccb89706e1
msgid "答：没有寻址加密，同频都可以收到。"
msgstr "A: It does not support addressing or encryption. Devices on the same frequency can receive the data."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:29 f7a30e816a3c46dd9df51a0a861efbc9
msgid "LoRa模块如何进入低功耗模式（睡眠模式），低功耗模式下功耗是多少？"
msgstr "How can a LoRa module enter low-power mode (sleep mode)? What is the power consumption in low-power mode?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:30 a7d9288a39d64e7cbce296d1447e04f8
msgid "通过SPI通信写寄存器的方式进入低功耗模式，低功耗模式下电流为0.2uA（微安μA）------注：此方法不适用Ra-06"
msgstr "Enter low-power mode by writing registers through SPI communication. The current in low-power mode is 0.2uA.  ------Note: This method does not apply to Ra-06."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:33 d5a3ea7c615d4e9f823ebc34b5121f64
msgid "LoRa模块上使用的是普通晶体还是TCXO石英晶体，频点为多少？"
msgstr "Does the LoRa module use a normal crystal or a TCXO crystal? What is the frequency?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:34 c614f59a91dd4e6e89230794518e8293
msgid "答：使用的是普通晶体，频点为32Mhz"
msgstr "A: It uses a normal crystal with a frequency of 32MHz."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:37 77a75c88b1ba4a16951df184e604b9fb
msgid "关于SX1278射频模式切换的引脚要如何设置？"
msgstr "How should the pins for SX1278 RF mode switching be configured?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:38 e3c043a507bf4f72aa29fdfd869d5be0
msgid "答：LoRa模组没有射频开关芯片，不支持这样切换，直接通过SPI配置寄存器就可以使用LoRa模组"
msgstr "A: The LoRa module does not have an RF switch chip and does not support this type of switching. You can use the LoRa module directly by configuring registers through SPI."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:41 bec9dc1e505149d492c49b1715590216
msgid "不同的LoRa模块之间通信，可以给LoRa模块加地址吗，用来区分是哪一个LoRa模块?"
msgstr "Can LoRa modules communicate with each other? Can an address be added to distinguish which LoRa module it is?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:42 fd8521b9ac43477d86f84b5716e43b12
msgid "答：可以，在有效负载的前两个字节定义为地址"
msgstr "A: Yes. You can define the first two bytes of the payload as the address."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:45 2ff152303841437aa2899c6aae4da5d8
msgid "信号带宽（BW），符号速率（Rs）和数据速率（DR）间的关系是什么？"
msgstr "What is the relationship between signal bandwidth (BW), symbol rate (Rs), and data rate (DR)?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:46 50b87f86eb1c4609a6427e8cdac9e62b
msgid "Rs=BW/(2^SF)、DR= SF*( BW/2^SF)*CR，但我们建议你使用Semtech LoRa调制解调器计算器按照不同的配置选型评估数据速率和传输时间。"
msgstr "Rs = BW / (2^SF), DR = SF * (BW / 2^SF) * CR. However, we recommend using the Semtech LoRa Modem Calculator to evaluate the data rate and transmission time according to different configurations."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:49 5dd19a8cbd5f4d3da6538bea95dd70e8
msgid "LoRa设备天线上可以达到的实际Tx功率是多少？"
msgstr "What is the actual Tx power that can be achieved at the antenna of a LoRa device?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:50 0ee1a9be90d8413ea7b34febee6f9d92
msgid "在芯片引脚输出的功率是+20dBm，经过匹配/滤波损耗后在天线后，在天线上功  率是+19dBm +/-0.5dB。最大输出功率在不同的地区有不同的规定，LoRaWAN规范定义了不同地区不同的输出功率使链路预算最大化。"
msgstr "The output power at the chip pin is +20dBm. After matching/filtering loss, the power at the antenna is +19dBm +/-0.5dB. The maximum output power is regulated differently in different regions. The LoRaWAN specification defines different output powers for different regions to maximize the link budget."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:53 61c40c98cd8d495298d45fa1d93a6479
msgid "当两个LoRa模块不能相互通信时，故障检测的步骤是什么？"
msgstr "What are the troubleshooting steps when two LoRa modules cannot communicate with each other?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:54 279b474c4e8c448aab13e86827ad0a12
msgid "答：首先，在两个设备间检查由晶振引起的频率偏移。带宽（BW）、中心频率和数据速率这些都源自晶振频率。其次，检查在两边的软件/固件设置，确保频率、带宽、扩频因子、编码率和数据包结构是一致的。"
msgstr "A: First, check the frequency offset caused by the crystal oscillator between the two devices. Bandwidth (BW), center frequency, and data rate are all derived from the crystal frequency. Second, check the software/firmware settings on both sides to ensure that the frequency, bandwidth, spreading factor, coding rate, and packet structure are consistent."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:57 a711e8af97424114b4c552625bbff211
msgid "LoRa模块可以发送或者接受一个无限长度的有效载荷数据包吗？"
msgstr "Can a LoRa module send or receive a payload packet of unlimited length?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:58 14e22e53ab02425798e4ece451de0c5d
msgid "答：不可以，在LoRa发送或者接受中最大数据包长度是256个字节"
msgstr "A: No. In LoRa transmission or reception, the maximum packet length is 256 bytes."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:61 89f643510e32416aa876bf235868aff7
msgid "LoRa模式的有效载荷长度可以用任意数据配置为256个字节吗？"
msgstr "Can the payload length in LoRa mode be configured to 256 bytes with arbitrary data?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:62 32b82cc72aee469aaab9bb3ea7b64344
msgid "答：SX127x LoRa设备在LoRa模式中有一个256字节的FIFO。理论上，所有的256字                 节都可以用于TX或RX。然而，用低数据速率配置，256字节有效载荷的传输时          间将会很长（几秒或更长），这对于抗衰落和高干扰环境是不好的。在大多数环境             中这不是一个健壮的配置，因此建议如果想要一个使用低数据速率长的有效载荷，            那么数据包可以分成几个短的数据包。"
msgstr "A: SX127x LoRa devices have a 256-byte FIFO in LoRa mode. In theory, all 256 bytes can be used for TX or RX. However, with a low data rate configuration, the transmission time for a 256-byte payload will be very long, several seconds or more, which is not good for anti-fading and high-interference environments. In most environments this is not a robust configuration. Therefore, if a long payload is required at a low data rate, it is recommended to split the packet into several shorter packets."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:65 75b0795d49e3484685e8ae8d943f4f3f
msgid "LoRa网关的容量是多少？一个网关可以连接多少个节点？"
msgstr "What is the capacity of a LoRa gateway? How many nodes can one gateway connect to?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:66 7a6694b5970e4639b7bd45adff829014
msgid "答：首先最重要的是，容量是在一定时间内节接受数据包数量的一个结果。一个SX1301       有8个通道，使用LoRaWAN协议每天可以接受接近150万包数据。因此，如果你的应用每小时发送一个包，那么一个SX1301网关可以处理大约62500个终端设备。"
msgstr "A: Most importantly, capacity is determined by the number of packets received within a certain period of time. An SX1301 has 8 channels and can receive nearly 1.5 million packets per day using the LoRaWAN protocol. Therefore, if your application sends one packet per hour, one SX1301 gateway can handle about 62,500 end devices."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:69 c2813161a0354294b830cfd701a444d7
msgid "如果不能达到+20dBm，如何解决输出功率问题？"
msgstr "If +20dBm cannot be achieved, how should the output power issue be resolved?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:70 1ad2857492ca4c8490cd8c325b44af29
msgid "答：1.请确认你连接到正确的引脚（PA_Boost）设置，20dBm输出的引脚。每个频段有两个输出端口。一个是高功率端口称为PA_boost，另一个是高效端口称为RFO。"
msgstr "A: 1. Confirm that you are connected to the correct pin, PA_Boost, for 20dBm output. Each frequency band has two output ports. One is the high-power port called PA_Boost, and the other is the high-efficiency port called RFO."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:71 f396d7b7aacf45f9bfa574fc39660e83
msgid "2. 然后，检测软件配置。应该正确地配置好三个寄存器：RegPaConfig、RegOcp 和 RegPaDac。这意味着你在软件中应选择正确的引脚做相应的输出，再依据你需要的功耗级别设置正确的值 3. 确认他们与Semtech参考设计相一致以便设计一个好的PCB布局。这对于可能达到最大的输出功率来说是重要的。"
msgstr "2. Then check the software configuration. Three registers should be configured correctly: RegPaConfig, RegOcp, and RegPaDac. This means that the correct pin should be selected in the software for the corresponding output, and the correct values should be set according to the required power consumption level. 3. Confirm that the design is consistent with the Semtech reference design in order to achieve a good PCB layout. This is important for reaching the maximum possible output power."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:75 4287442823a64f1f98fd5f5cccc23887
msgid "LoRa通信距离和什么有关？"
msgstr "What factors affect LoRa communication distance?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:76 ba32296e84af4503853d6e84fd7dfb51
msgid "1，发射功率。 2，天线角度，通常天线应该相互平行。 3，天线的中心频率是否与模块通讯频率匹配。每个天线都有一定的频率范围，称为带宽，在这个范围内，天线阻抗最小，效率最高，这个范围的中间最佳点即中心频率，驻波比最小。 4，LoRa的配置参数。空中速率越高，LoRa发送数据的速率越快，但是接收灵敏度就降低了。所以要提高通讯距离，就需要适当降低空中速率。空中速率大小和扩频因子SF、带宽BW、编码率有关。空中速率与扩频因子、编码率大小反相关，与带宽正相关。例如，远距离测试时，参数可以这样设置：扩频因子:12；带宽BW:6；编码率:2，注意在低速率通讯时，开启LoRa低速率优化功能。 5，程序错误。典型的是PA设置错误，LoRa 1278/1276有三个射频信号发送口，分别是RFO_LF: 低频率发送口，效率高；PA_BOOST: 20dBm信号放大口，安信可的Ra01,Ra02使用的是该发送口，程序里务必开启；RFO_HF: 高频率发送口，效率高 根据硬件原理图连接，选择相应的发送口。"
msgstr "1. Transmit power. 2. Antenna angle. Usually the antennas should be parallel to each other. 3. Whether the center frequency of the antenna matches the communication frequency of the module. Each antenna has a certain frequency range, called bandwidth. Within this range, the antenna impedance is the lowest and the efficiency is the highest. The best point in the middle of this range is the center frequency, where the standing wave ratio is the lowest. 4. LoRa configuration parameters. The higher the air data rate, the faster LoRa sends data, but the receiving sensitivity decreases. Therefore, to increase communication distance, the air data rate should be reduced appropriately. The air data rate is related to spreading factor SF, bandwidth BW, and coding rate. The air data rate is negatively correlated with the spreading factor and coding rate, and positively correlated with bandwidth. For example, for long-distance testing, the parameters can be set as follows: spreading factor: 12; bandwidth BW: 6; coding rate: 2. Note that when communicating at a low data rate, the LoRa low data rate optimization function should be enabled. 5. Program errors. A typical issue is incorrect PA configuration. LoRa 1278/1276 has three RF signal transmission ports: RFO_LF, a low-frequency transmission port with high efficiency; PA_BOOST, a 20 dBm signal amplification port, which is used by Ai-Thinker Ra-01 and Ra-02 and must be enabled in the program; and RFO_HF, a high-frequency transmission port with high efficiency. Select the corresponding transmission port according to the hardware schematic connection."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:84 959138b1b5a84fe39672ebb8c836afc5
msgid "Ra-01这个可以用线连单片机吗？"
msgstr "Can Ra-01 be connected to an MCU with wires?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:85 89849de8ef2246afab0e95a6fc39e799
msgid "答：可以   通过单片机的SPI协议进行驱动"
msgstr "A: Yes. It can be driven through the MCU's SPI protocol."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:88 b687a0dab97f4f5aa574398b70c9416c
msgid "\"RHF76-052可以传输多远"
msgstr "How far can RHF76-052 transmit?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:89 b817d80d1866491d84067e3ac53cbe60
msgid "答：2公里"
msgstr "A: 2km."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:92 a174a7a4e86a432bbaac76774ba1e018
msgid "Ra-06 里边的 MCU，我们能用来开发传感器吗"
msgstr "Can we use the MCU inside Ra-06 to develop sensors?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:93 f0cbd57f3a814809955485ceb56bcb49
msgid "\"答：不支持二次开发"
msgstr "A: Secondary development is not supported."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:96 ac34e1b68a154a02919e33af28145637
msgid "LoRa测试板底座的功能是什么"
msgstr "What is the function of the LoRa test board base?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:97 689caeaaec5f424aa4772ad753ee5790
msgid "\"答：MCU驱动LoRa模块，MCU型号是STC15W408AS"
msgstr "A: The MCU drives the LoRa module. The MCU model is STC15W408AS."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:100 a46f65bdb37249eda5252ef8e1ae0bd9
msgid "模块的使用的晶振是多少MHz的？ 能否提供STM32的demo代码"
msgstr "What MHz crystal does the module use? Can STM32 demo code be provided?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:101 c364dff7d9d94b60ae681a7a7bfd3ff2
msgid "32晶振，我们官网有STM32的代码哈"
msgstr "It uses a 32MHz crystal. STM32 code is available on our official website."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:104 947b82bc82d04d17bbb374ff2fd8da16
msgid "Ra-02支持点对多吗 ？支持一对多吗"
msgstr "Does Ra-02 support point-to-multipoint? Does it support one-to-many communication?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:105 0fc8c24e09da4fcba44e3c56a8746036
msgid "支持，只要同频"
msgstr "Yes, as long as they are on the same frequency."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:108 992753386498471fb81423e0de27db9e
msgid "Ra-01与Ra-02增益大概有多少？"
msgstr "What is the approximate gain of Ra-01 and Ra-02?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:109 f82878a6b090434db85dbd9599b81d8b
msgid "1.5db"
msgstr "1.5dB."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:112 b64338da58f441b6a043e8b776391cda
msgid "Ra-01模组上的晶振是多少频率的？需要这个参数"
msgstr "What is the frequency of the crystal on the Ra-01 module? This parameter is needed."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:113 e9ff9313f20643c390b5ba13ae50eafe
msgid "使用的是普通晶体，频点为32Mhz"
msgstr "It uses a normal crystal with a frequency of 32MHz."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:116 f5610f202a0349cb88952e8d93d7ad24
msgid "Ra-01和Ra-02距离是多远"
msgstr "What is the communication distance of Ra-01 and Ra-02?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:117 34a937597ba742648e9d52a422544838
msgid "正常可以达到3km"
msgstr "Normally it can reach 3km."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:120 000ff6696ac54677ada4b0b13d6e16a5
msgid "Ra-06可以和LoRa网关配合吗 ？RHF76-052可以吗 ？Ra06只能点对点传输"
msgstr "Can Ra-06 work with a LoRa gateway? Can RHF76-052? Is Ra-06 only for point-to-point transmission?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:121 eecc5c4f77144688883edbceebdb95c9
msgid "不行，点对点通信，或者用一个Ra-06作为网关端开发使用"
msgstr "No. It supports point-to-point communication, or one Ra-06 can be used as the gateway side for development."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:124 c288e40d34c442a98f1b7c5298148711
msgid "LoRa的模块有集中器的么"
msgstr "Does the LoRa module have a concentrator?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:125 affe1490cad14e7f963366f79c1eb01d
msgid "没有 ，这个只是一个射频芯片"
msgstr "No, it's just an RF chip."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:128 96a5a3f62abf433b87a0db082231d15b
msgid "Ra-02模块与MCU通信是什么协议？"
msgstr "What protocol is used for communication between the Ra-02 module and the MCU?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:129 f07867730be1401481ffa522e8845142
msgid "SPI协议"
msgstr "SPI protocol."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:132 efc219e765c3474a95de44467ac244ec
msgid "Ra-01模组能配置成20dB的发射功率吗？我看你们模组上标的是pa+18dB，最大发射功率是18dB?"
msgstr "Can the Ra-01 module be configured to 20dB transmit power? I see that the module is marked as PA +18dB. Is the maximum transmit power 18dB?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:133 080688b58dda4516b45d449947689011
msgid "可以配置成20dB，但是实际有线损，实际上是少一点的"
msgstr "It can be configured to 20dB, but there is actual cable loss, so the actual power is slightly lower."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:136 8585bf7657c24e17a96a4b3990646907
msgid "Ra-02支持470MHZ吗？"
msgstr "Does Ra-02 support 470MHz?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:137 ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:291 ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:497 09c15edd597e45fd9264126b2d537c55 15431844172d4d008313bd0bd00c4052 d5343af1a74f4f7aa1787f7c29d514e2
msgid "支持的"
msgstr "Yes, it does."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:140 93cfbc3ee7d740c6a9abf52fdd1319f9
msgid "Ra-01与Ra-02支持自组网吗"
msgstr "Do Ra-01 and Ra-02 support self-organizing networks?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:141 66d8f2a4e98e4d3eadcbf93c8d7ec5fa
