msgstr "The communication distance can be extended. A rod antenna is recommended, and it should be a rod antenna for the dedicated frequency band. Also pay attention to the actual environment. Walls or buildings may block and interfere with the signal."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:184 d4097e89cfa2442e81e36960f88e15d3
msgid "你们没有SPI接口的LoRa模块吗"
