msgid "Ra-06模块的硬件资料"
msgstr "Hardware materials for the Ra-06 module"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:889 a679c4a189804631a5322464d14bdd9c
msgid "https://docs.ai-thinker.com/_media/LoRa/hardware/Ra-06_v1.3.zip"
msgstr "https://docs.ai-thinker.com/_media/LoRa/hardware/Ra-06_v1.3.zip"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:892 13cad27b3cee402d8b42cad695c8304a
msgid "Ra-07和Ra-08有什么主要的区别"
msgstr "What are the main differences between Ra-07 and Ra-08?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:893 7bd82ddbff2942bd8b3f449d7a41e0b1
msgid "Ra-08除了支持jink烧写外还支持串口烧写，方便做二次开发使用"
msgstr "In addition to supporting J-Link programming, Ra-08 also supports UART programming, which makes secondary development easier."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:896 1fec96724ef24293af6b8f43b7f5261d
msgid "LoRa模块可以组网不"
msgstr "Can LoRa modules form a network?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:897 fcd4b349fc7045eba2348134d1a782c9
msgid "可以组网，但是组网功能相关代码逻辑需要自行实现"
msgstr "They can form a network, but the related networking code logic needs to be implemented by yourself."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:900 45c06a46e58f4799a0b75dc0f8aaa56a
msgid "LoRa模块影响通信速率和距离的两大重点原因是哪些。"
msgstr "What are the two key factors affecting LoRa communication rate and distance?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:901 6912c1a3177f48d48f648359d9bd8ea6
msgid "扩频因子和带宽，扩频因子越大距离越远，但是速率比较慢；带宽越宽速率越快，但是距离较近，两者相反。"
msgstr "Spreading factor and bandwidth. The larger the spreading factor, the longer the distance, but the slower the rate. The wider the bandwidth, the faster the rate, but the shorter the distance. The two are opposite."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:904 35ef75bc463c4d009dcc5df30fb0b917
msgid "LoRa模块一次最大可以传输多少个字节"
msgstr "What is the maximum number of bytes a LoRa module can transmit at one time?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:908 c2e11dc3926047caaa05a69282679457
msgid "Ra-08模块能否点对点通信"
msgstr "Can the Ra-08 module perform point-to-point communication?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:909 694151d5e5f74713a9d6a0df8df8aff0
msgid "出厂固件不支持，可以通过二次开发的方式进行实现"
msgstr "The factory firmware does not support it. It can be implemented through secondary development."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:912 235805f01b084c0f806e5fc9dc67f288
msgid "Ra-01的测试板能给Ra-01S使用吗"
msgstr "Can the Ra-01 test board be used with Ra-01S?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:913 f125518cf1414cc1b8191192d1aec769
msgid "不能，因为驱动不同"
msgstr "No, because the drivers are different."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:916 64798242a546406da1f723bf47e8cf09
msgid "Ra-08烧录串口和通讯串口的发送引脚是否共用"
msgstr "Are the programming UART and communication UART TX pins of Ra-08 shared?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:917 ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1214 c94d354c40ce497680bbb12ebf54fc6a f1393e0f9f8e4333ab4d34f9f3e65c4e
msgid "共用"
msgstr "They are shared."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:920 ad96ce07f6844db68dc0fca050fb333d
msgid "Ra-01以及Ra-01S模组的引脚驱动有区别吗？"
msgstr "Are there differences in the pin drivers of Ra-01 and Ra-01S modules?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:921 ee27b8107d3042c7afe3a4df0577b98c
msgid "有的，Ra-01模组中断提示引脚为DIO0，而Ra-01S则用DIO1以及busy结合；"
msgstr "Yes. The interrupt indication pin of the Ra-01 module is DIO0, while Ra-01S uses DIO1 together with BUSY."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:924 4c6b4f19754b4cacba91ee8dede004e4
msgid "Ra08模块出厂固件支持点对点传输吗"
msgstr "Does the factory firmware of the Ra-08 module support point-to-point transmission?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:925 c1d6e88b5d8b4d5c8a624298c3114345
msgid "不支持，出厂固件仅支持与LoRawan网关进行通信，如需点对点传输得需要二次开发实现"
msgstr "No. The factory firmware only supports communication with a LoRaWAN gateway. For point-to-point transmission, secondary development is required."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:928 dfa9014cead140a995fdea5a286b6ba3
msgid "Ra-01S模块在使用的时候是否需要接上TXEN RXEN引脚"
msgstr "Does the Ra-01S module need TXEN and RXEN connected during use?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:929 0b868d21b324423e8d3c5c0f3e435914
msgid "不需要，我们通过软件控制射频收发，不需要硬件控制"
msgstr "No. We control RF transmit/receive through software, so hardware control is not required."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:932 496f65eb4a8f4fd699b6619dcc82783b
msgid "Ra-01、02模块支持自定义LoRawan通讯协议吗"
msgstr "Do Ra-01 and Ra-02 modules support custom LoRaWAN communication protocols?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:933 f43c29110f5a430596e04fb6f025a541
msgid "支持，可以在MCU上实现LoRawan相关的功能"
msgstr "Yes. LoRaWAN-related functions can be implemented on the MCU."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:936 1914307ab9ab4b528071d9e7d1ae6e48
msgid "Ra-07、08模组能否当LoRawan网关使用"
msgstr "Can Ra-07 and Ra-08 modules be used as LoRaWAN gateways?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:937 a9df708d8c3d4960997dd532fbfa7336
msgid "不能，单模组仅支持LoRawan节点"
msgstr "No. A single module only supports LoRaWAN node functionality."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:940 9ce30d3544dc4141ba74497f7534930f
msgid "Ra-01S和SC上的TXEN、RXEN引脚是做什么用处"
msgstr "What are the TXEN and RXEN pins on Ra-01S and SC used for?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:941 d57c804e03594b35bead3c2cf2b05970
msgid "这个是射频天线开关引脚，控制射频收发使用"
msgstr "They are RF antenna switch pins, used to control RF transmit and receive."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:944 d8a705f038d0491a8404b73955d36d94
msgid "Ra-08H支持AS923频段吗"
msgstr "Does Ra-08H support the AS923 band?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:945 0a5b5b07fdff49568ed456e8eea3fa71
msgid "支持，需要烧写支持AS923频段的固件"
msgstr "Yes. Firmware supporting the AS923 band needs to be flashed."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:948 4fb397eee1124923a5e063a0f01831b5
msgid "Ra-07/08LoraWan模组有几个接收通道"
msgstr "How many receive channels do Ra-07/08 LoRaWAN modules have?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:949 827567e1751f47c5b794e1b43ee43dd9
msgid "8个。"
msgstr "8."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:952 3eb082c8974f4487bb334d9bab16d7db
msgid "Ra-01S和SC跑官方驱动需要接TXEN,RXEN引脚吗"
msgstr "Do Ra-01S and SC need TXEN/RXEN pins when running the official driver?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:953 7774135521784a5ba26b3a4655c26437
msgid "不需要，接线除了常规的SPI引脚外，只需要接RESET,DIO1,BUSY引脚"
msgstr "No. In addition to the regular SPI pins, only RESET, DIO1, and BUSY need to be connected."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:956 4ad726c132f445b7bc151771c2fd2afc
msgid "Ra-08模组能当网关使用吗"
msgstr "Can the Ra-08 module be used as a gateway?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:957 d3a35a423dcc47a8b4f5c9273c97047d
msgid "不能，模组只能当节点使用，不能当网关"
msgstr "No. The module can only be used as a node, not as a gateway."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:960 7dea24b5f87d4436989db721b0537f33
msgid "LoRa的通讯方式是全双工还是半双工"
msgstr "Is LoRa communication full-duplex or half-duplex?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:961 12d2b6f8716b41b98925fc9825fe8afe
msgid "半双工的方式"
msgstr "Half-duplex."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:964 57702702e3f6461db4bbaf3061811d23
msgid "LoRa模块不配天线有什么影响"
msgstr "What happens if a LoRa module is used without an antenna?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:965 61bb0b74a60f437e9e50647898a57783
msgid "模块没有天线会出现距离短 经常丢包的情况"
msgstr "Without an antenna, the module will have a short range and frequent packet loss."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:968 8fc44f68abf147eb8c6c841297f73250
msgid "有带中继功能的LoRa模组么？"
msgstr "Are there any LoRa modules with relay functionality?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:969 38af63b860384e659d1fec9ecbd74003
msgid "LoRa模组可实现中继功能，但需要客户自行设计该功能"
msgstr "LoRa modules can implement relay functionality, but customers need to design this function themselves."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:972 51633ef606574a2d9f39672fbc343dc4
msgid "Ra-08的二次开发的demo编译好的固件烧录地址设置为什么？"
msgstr "What should the flashing address be for the compiled firmware of the Ra-08 secondary-development demo?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:973 81ff3c08103e41e1be23052e8e3604a4
msgid "烧录地址为0x08000000"
msgstr "The flashing address is 0x08000000."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:976 88996d3762e44a98bb64ada082e63526
msgid "Ra-08H模组为何无法入网TTN，用的网关是US915网段？"
msgstr "Why cannot the Ra-08H module join TTN when the gateway uses the US915 band?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:977 f29e4930503043b282eb1838c5a9ca53
msgid "查清楚，a、模组是否已经烧录了US915网段的固件；b、查下模组的掩码配置是否与网关一致"
msgstr "Check the following: a. Whether the module has been flashed with US915-band firmware; b. Whether the module mask configuration matches the gateway."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:980 eb524a0cbfc64aeebba0519ec8d76e8e
msgid "Ra-08模组在上电可看到log信息，但是发送AT指令没有反应是什么原因呢？"
msgstr "Why can the Ra-08 module show log information after power-on, but does not respond to AT commands?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:981 19aad5f89f154c03854eb940f8aa54c2
msgid "RX口没有选择LPRXD接口"
msgstr "The RX port has not been selected as the LPRXD interface."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:984 fb116690be984780b0fdd834c1840cef
msgid "Ra-01模组与Ra-02模组的转接板是否兼容的呢"
msgstr "Are the adapter boards of the Ra-01 module and Ra-02 module compatible?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:985 dd147dea4b2d4292a43904a8e3eebff6
msgid "转接板兼容Ra-01、Ra-02、Ra-01H、Ra-01S、Ra-01SH以及Ra-01SC模组，单驱动引脚的解析不完全一样"
msgstr "The adapter board is compatible with Ra-01, Ra-02, Ra-01H, Ra-01S, Ra-01SH, and Ra-01SC modules, but the driver pins are not parsed exactly the same."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:988 d6285e90e59746498f148e205b443416
msgid "Ra-01SH默认不带IPEX座子，补上IPEX座子能插IPEX线使用吗？"
msgstr "Ra-01SH does not have an IPEX connector by default. Can an IPEX cable be used after adding the IPEX connector?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:989 22f78b0306ab4cf0be96da15be37bc4b
msgid "补上IPEX座子能插IPEX线"
msgstr "After adding the IPEX connector, an IPEX cable can be used."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:992 8b0d1c426a4445d9a06409a6e36f640d
msgid "Ra-08模块在设计上需要注意哪些引脚"
msgstr "Which pins should be noted in the design of the Ra-08 module?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:993 799d660fac6141858f4a6b3420f8b1a7
msgid "IO2引脚和IO11引脚，IO2为烧录引脚，正常使用需要保持低电平或者悬空，IO11引脚为系统引脚，正常使用必须为高电平或者悬空"
msgstr "IO2 and IO11. IO2 is the programming pin and should be kept low or floating during normal use. IO11 is a system pin and must be high or floating during normal use."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:996 466d80336b044cf69f6e14c2518623fd
msgid "Ra-01S中的DIO1不使用中断触发的形式，可以修改代码实现收发模式切换吗"
msgstr "If DIO1 on Ra-01S is not used as an interrupt trigger, can the code be modified to implement transmit/receive mode switching?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:997 bdae06e324314e368fbc9b9388d1fe13
msgid "可以通过修改代码实现，但是需对寄存器手册比较熟悉"
msgstr "Yes, it can be implemented by modifying the code, but you need to be familiar with the register manual."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1000 41bc4f5d25f34c0f9040306c3750b93a
msgid "LoRa测试底板能焊接哪些模组，使用上有什么需要注意的"
msgstr "Which modules can be soldered onto the LoRa test baseboard, and what should be noted during use?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1001 0ddd4faea50440e7be61d43395c2fb02
msgid "测试底板能焊接Ra-01/02/01S/01SC等模组，其中，Ra-01/02在STM32例程上需要接DIO0引脚，Ra-01S/SC需要接DIO1和BUSY引脚"
msgstr "The test baseboard can be soldered with Ra-01/02/01S/01SC and other modules. When using the STM32 example, Ra-01/02 need to connect the DIO0 pin, while Ra-01S/SC need to connect DIO1 and BUSY pins."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1004 228c712fb43b410c99fe9c79effd3083
msgid "Ra-08开发板的Class B入网方式，重启的情况下数据无法传输到服务器，显示计数不对，是为何？"
msgstr "For Ra-08 development board Class B join mode, why cannot data be transmitted to the server after restart, and why does it show a counter mismatch?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1005 fcef018906244d37a1f0cb661231d0b5
msgid "Class B入网方式不需要做入网动作，因此重启的情况下，计数将重置为0，而服务器的计数值不变，因此，一旦计数值对不上，服务器将丢弃该数据。"
msgstr "Class B join mode does not require a join operation. Therefore, after restart, the counter is reset to 0, while the server counter remains unchanged. Once the counters do not match, the server discards the data."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1008 3fdb7ee8c147407288a9e6824a40a1ea
msgid "Ra-02模组的ipex接口是什么规格的？"
msgstr "What specification is the IPEX interface on the Ra-02 module?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1009 da36ceb07dcb490d85d4f6127fd18adc
msgid "我司所有带IPEX底座的模组均是搭配的IPEX 1代底座。"
msgstr "All modules from our company with IPEX sockets use IPEX generation 1 sockets."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1012 60759e2f58a94caf837f110f6aae4cfd
msgid "Ra-02模组我不小心用螺丝刀碰一下就没信号了，但是如果MCU重启又有信号了，是什么原因呢？"
msgstr "I accidentally touched the Ra-02 module with a screwdriver and it lost signal, but the signal returns after MCU restart. What is the reason?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1013 2ed15d1434674c72be1971b5703e4db2
msgid "天线短路了，需分离之后重置射频发射或者接收功能。"
msgstr "The antenna was short-circuited. It needs to be separated and then the RF transmit or receive function should be reset."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1016 4055d8b106d24508a57ece1675a56fd1
msgid "Ra-08中的SPI引脚是否就是规格书中标注的SSP引脚？"
msgstr "Are the SPI pins on Ra-08 the SSP pins marked in the specification?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1017 c3391bf9a36e4fedb4ead6b5327859bc
msgid "是的。"
msgstr "Yes."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1020 8c61a76f60744f11bb99b244068eb6a7
msgid "Ra-01模块内置的SX1278芯片，在初始化配置时PA输出引脚应当设置为RFO还是PA_BOOST"
msgstr "For the SX1278 chip built into the Ra-01 module, should the PA output pin be configured as RFO or PA_BOOST during initialization?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1021 efbf59f4a2fd48759148a87bd2e8001e
msgid "设置PA_BOOST"
msgstr "Set it to PA_BOOST."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1024 9a05ef9d0508484c929d44cd003b1380
msgid "Ra-01S模块内部芯片外部有没有加PA放大器"
msgstr "Does the Ra-01S module have an external PA amplifier added outside the internal chip?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1025 647e329caa834bfeaff238752761e445
msgid "没有添加放大器"
msgstr "No amplifier is added."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1028 012302d8880f42b08bc95b4a10736d36
msgid "LoRa模块能否用在水表上"
msgstr "Can LoRa modules be used in water meters?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1032 792c4004e884452dbd7f38b770904c52
msgid "有没有不限包长度的lora模组"
msgstr "Are there any LoRa modules with unlimited packet length?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1033 8afad46c18724c3ab9a938dd0915afec
msgid "目前lora模块最大包长度为250个字节，没有不限包长度的"
msgstr "Currently, the maximum packet length of LoRa modules is 250 bytes. There is no module with unlimited packet length."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1036 1d966c8b7ce24e79853616722c606797
msgid "请问Ra-08模组支持设置扩频因子么？"
msgstr "Does the Ra-08 module support setting the spreading factor?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1037 55c5aa00a9bd43f0a239b5431d2ffb97
msgid "支持通过AT指令设置扩频因子，在设置之前实现关闭ADR功能；"
msgstr "Yes. The spreading factor can be set through AT commands. ADR must be disabled before setting it."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1040 3ff42073daf3431b9d2d9f8dcde3485f
msgid "Ra-08模块能否当网关使用"
msgstr "Can the Ra-08 module be used as a gateway?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1041 0a9ee92fc81e473e92ba34f8e4807409
msgid "不能，只能当节点"
msgstr "No. It can only be used as a node."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1044 8199a8c2adf4465a9a075dd9d652fee1
msgid "RG-02支持连接helium平台吗"
msgstr "Does RG-02 support connection to the Helium platform?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1048 1f0f7574cefc4f3fadab2f94fd40ddc2
msgid "LoRa模块的信号能穿透铁皮盒子吗"
msgstr "Can the signal of a LoRa module penetrate an iron box?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1049 5b99a99121f14f03bc14a5d17094d43e
msgid "不能穿透，信号会被铁皮盒子吸收"
msgstr "No. The signal cannot penetrate it; it will be absorbed by the iron box."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1052 0c848206e4ec49ee821c89dfb9333f8f
msgid "Ra-01SC模块如果不使用IPEX座子，可以直接焊接天线引脚引天线出来吗"
msgstr "If the Ra-01SC module does not use the IPEX connector, can the antenna pin be directly soldered to lead out the antenna?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/LoRa-LoRaWan/index.rst:1053 19009939146d47af83bd01ee8086617c
msgid "可以焊接，因为座子和天线引脚是导通的"
